message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY. The paper describes a dataset of curated facts and crowd-sourced multiple-choice questions, which are relevant to natural language processing and machine learning tasks such as information extraction, question answering, and lexical semantic modelling. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
